<h3>3.获取过滤数据</h3>
<div class="dp-highlighter">
<div class="bar"></div>
<ol class="dp-j" start="1">
	<li class="alt"><span><span class="keyword">for</span><span> ( var x = </span><span class="number">0</span><span>; x &lt; canvasData.width; x++) {    </span></span></li>
	<li><span>         <span class="keyword">for</span><span> ( var y = </span><span class="number">0</span><span>; y &lt; canvasData.height; y++) {    </span></span></li>
	<li class="alt"><span>        </span></li>
	<li><span>           <span class="comment">// Index of the pixel in the array  </span><span>  </span></span></li>
	<li class="alt"><span>           var idx = (x + y * canvasData.width) * <span class="number">4</span><span>;    </span></span></li>
